msgid "Introduction to the course"
msgstr "Introducción al curso"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/epn/modules/ROOT/pages/introduction.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "Bienvenido"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/epn/modules/ROOT/pages/introduction.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "In this video (01:31), GBIF Executive Secretary, Joe Miller, shares his reflections on the importance of the network for GBIF’s success and the importance of this course as an opportunity towards formal engagment and establishing a Participant Node.   \n"
"If you are unable to watch the embedded Vimeo video, you can download it locally on the xref:downloads.adoc[Files for download] page.\n"
msgstr "En este vídeo (01:31), el Secretario Ejecutivo de GBIF, Joe Miller, comparte sus reflexiones sobre la importancia de la red para el éxito de GBIF y la relevancia de este curso para fomentar el compromiso formal y establecer un nodo Participante.   \n"
"Si no puede ver el vídeo incrustado de Vimeo, puede descargarlo desde la página xref:downloads.adoc[Files for download] page.\n"

